snippet.title: Reaction to the Johnny Depp & Amber Heard Situation
snippet.description:
A clip from the GZE podcast about Amber Heard and her abuse against her now ex-husband Johnny Depp. We introduce the newAmber Heard audio that came out about a week ago, talk about how many refused to believe Johnny a year ago, & how more women lying about situations like this can negatively affect future accusations that are actually true || Hit the like button if you enjoyed the video! Comment other topics or questions you'd like to see discussed/answered down below! || Tell those who are close to you how much they mean before they're gone
